    {
        "content": "<p>in this case i could use unfold, but i had a more complicated situation where i didnt want to unfold the term on the rhs, just on the lhs.</p>",
        "id": 530800034,
        "sender_full_name": "Klaus Gy",
        "timestamp": 1753457622
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If you want to isolate where you unfold, you can always use <code>conv</code> mode, like <code>conv =&gt; enter [1]; unfold foo</code></p>",
        "id": 530801025,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1753457991
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>thank you, that is helpful!</p>",
